  "prompt": "What is the best apps for learning how to sing english songs with audio check?",
  "response": "There are several apps that can help you learn to sing English songs and offer audio check features for feedback and improvement. Here are some of the popular options:\n\n1. **Smule**: This karaoke app allows you to sing along with various songs, record your performances, and get feedback on your singing. You can sing solo or collaborate with friends and other users.\n\n2. **Yousician**: While primarily focused on teaching musical instruments, Yousician also offers voice lessons. It provides real-time feedback on your pitch and timing.\n\n3. **SING! by Smule**: Another app by Smule, it offers vocal pitch and timing correction, useful features for singers looking to improve their performance.\n\n4. **Singscope**: This app provides a visual pitch detection tool that lets you see the pitch of your singing in real-time, helping you correct your pitch as you practice.\n\n5. **Voice Lessons (Learn to Sing)**: This app offers various exercises and songs to practice, with built-in tools to analyze your singing pitch and timing.\n\n6. **Vanido**: It offers personalized exercises based on your vocal range and provides feedback on pitch accuracy. It's excellent for daily vocal practice.\n\n7. **StarMaker**: Similar to Smule, it\u2019s a karaoke app that offers a wide range of songs to sing along with, and you can get feedback on your performances from the community.\n\n8. **Sing Sharp**: This app includes a pitch analyzer and various vocal exercises designed to improve your singing skills.\n\nThese apps can help you improve your singing by providing real-time feedback, pitch correction, and various exercises tailored to your skill level. Depending on your specific needs and preferences, you might find one app more suitable than others.",
